Expand Dashboard Widgets to See a Larger Version in Lightning Experience

Sometimes a chart or table is just a little too small. Open it in a window so you can see all the details.

To expand dashboard widgets:
Run Reports
Open a dashboard.
Hover over a widget and click .
A larger version of the dashboard widget overlays the dashboard. Optionally, click the left and right arrows to cycle through expanded versions of the dashboardâ€™s widget.
